Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.66,0:00:09.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个世界上的任何人都有没见过的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.13,0:00:22.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs20}轻松  漂亮  而柔和的表情  将她的心  轻轻地抓住
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.10,0:00:22.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都是骗人的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.35,0:00:26.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这种玩意
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.91,0:00:29.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.51,0:00:32.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs20}霉
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.45,0:00:33.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是什么啊  不是发霉了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.80,0:00:35.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,前不久才除过霉的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.98,0:00:38.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它很温柔非常甜美
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.70,0:00:39.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs20}抹布  抹布
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.00,0:00:42.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大概  如果可以看见的话
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.67,0:00:44.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谁都会想要的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.39,0:00:50.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正因为如此
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.00,0:00:52.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,世界才把它藏了起来
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.30,0:00:56.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了让人无法那么轻易地得到
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.97,0:00:59.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶  弄不掉
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.19,0:01:01.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs20}哼  但是
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.00,0:01:03.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs20}只要有高须棒的话
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.03,0:01:03.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是总有一天会有人找到
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.27,0:01:10.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,应该得到的那个唯一的人  一定能把它找出来
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.57,0:01:18.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就像这样  产生了羁绊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.63,0:02:57.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,生态生态生态  生态平衡
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.79,0:03:00.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小鹦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.20,0:03:03.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还在睡吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.72,0:03:05.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早上了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.85,0:03:07.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喵哈
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.69,0:03:09.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,捉住了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.70,0:03:18.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小龙  好冷淡哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.33,0:03:20.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天要上学  昨晚不是说过了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.05,0:03:25.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,开学典礼啊  恭喜你升级
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.65,0:03:28.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是对待迎接新学年的儿子的态度啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.71,0:03:29.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呐
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.74,0:03:31.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个房间好黑哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.25,0:03:32.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,帮忙把窗帘拉开来
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.77,0:03:33.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经拉开了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.72,0:03:40.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好大的公寓啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.22,0:03:42.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是什么样的家伙住着呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.76,0:03:45.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个建成之后  阳光的恩惠被夺去
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.60,0:03:47.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,害得换洗的衣服都很难干
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.90,0:03:50.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,每天每天  发霉发霉发霉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.58,0:03:52.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这敏锐眼神
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.25,0:03:54.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小龙越来越像你爸爸了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.60,0:03:57.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,越来越像了  越来越像了…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.34,0:03:59.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别把我和那人…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.42,0:04:01.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  好帅哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.82,0:04:04.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,更加跟你爸爸一模一样了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.48,0:04:07.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.61,0:04:09.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小龙已经要走了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.54,0:04:11.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的早饭呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.94,0:04:13.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在老地方
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.28,0:04:15.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.27,0:04:19.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只有那个
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.75,0:04:22.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是绝对不想被那么说的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.09,0:04:28.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就因为你所称赞的这个眼神
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.27,0:04:30.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.37,0:04:31.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.31,0:04:32.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.30,0:04:37.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,高高高  高须同学
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.93,0:04:39.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在干什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.20,0:04:40.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不  我不是故意的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.91,0:04:40.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎  什么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.36,0:04:40.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.00,0:04:42.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,收下这个饶了我们吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.82,0:04:43.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.31,0:04:44.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在就只有这个了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.92,0:04:45.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是真的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.82,0:04:47.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个应该可以了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.29,0:04:47.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.24,0:04:49.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.90,0:04:52.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好可怕  那就是杀人之眼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.31,0:04:53.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.96,0:05:00.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs20}失物寄放  大桥高校杂务处
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.79,0:05:03.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又是你  你真的总是捡到钱包呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.30,0:05:06.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呐  还在同一个班就好了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.08,0:05:06.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.38,0:05:11.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.19,0:05:13.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了是同班
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.94,0:05:21.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,糟糕了  又…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.38,0:05:21.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哟
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.63,0:05:25.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今年又是同班了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.29,0:05:26.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,高须
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.53,0:05:27.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,北村
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.08,0:05:31.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,本年度的开学典礼到此结束
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.91,0:05:35.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请回到各自的教室  做好班会的准备
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.72,0:05:37.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,新的班级
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.55,0:05:40.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又得从解除大家的误会开始才行么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.11,0:05:42.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.13,0:05:44.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,至少不是所有人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.34,0:05:46.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是知道的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.79,0:05:50.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  谢谢了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.78,0:05:51.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.15,0:05:54.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也有像这样理解我的人在呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.71,0:05:56.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且在这个班里…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.44,0:05:57.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哟  北村同学
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.47,0:06:01.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今年也是同班呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.30,0:06:02.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦  栉枝
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.61,0:06:03.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也是C班啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.81,0:06:07.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是高须同学是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.30,0:06:08.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还记得我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.75,0:06:11.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像经常在北村同学周围碰到你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.37,0:06:15.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,栉  栉枝实乃梨对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.97,0:06:17.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀哎呀真是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.48,0:06:19.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,居然记得我的全名
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.81,0:06:21.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我好高兴啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.43,0:06:25.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么那么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.42,0:06:29.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就让我们一起清爽开朗地享受青春吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.78,0:06:30.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.54,0:06:31.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦…哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.00,0:06:34.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就这样  那个就…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.28,0:06:37.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了  高须
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.69,0:06:38.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.35,0:06:40.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,稍  稍微去一下洗手间
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.25,0:06:40.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.27,0:06:42.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我先走了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.01,0:06:51.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这么快就颠峰对决了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.49,0:06:52.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个人和逢坂大河
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.04,0:06:55.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,突然就开始决赛了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.54,0:06:57.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,新旧老大争夺战么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.87,0:07:00.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.39,0:07:02.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好小的身体
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.06,0:07:04.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,像人偶一样
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.80,0:07:06.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是  好像…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.49,0:07:10.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么感觉微妙地给人以威慑
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.50,0:07:12.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像一不小心就会被吃掉一样
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.02,0:07:14.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个  这个是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.64,0:07:15.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.64,0:07:17.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不良高须和掌中老虎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.64,0:07:17.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs20}注：「大河」与「老虎」日文发音相同
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.89,0:07:18.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.29,0:07:21.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(120,30)\fs22}像老虎一样凶猛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.90,0:07:21.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(520,30)\fs22}但是很小
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.06,0:07:21.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,掌中老虎？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.98,0:07:23.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.31,0:07:24.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,掌中老…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.81,0:07:27.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.97,0:07:29.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,名副其实…不是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.07,0:07:35.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好  那么今天就到这里
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.90,0:07:39.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有交志愿调查表的同学等会儿到办公室来哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.12,0:07:41.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好…好吗  高须同学
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.03,0:07:43.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.92,0:07:48.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事吧  大河
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.66,0:07:50.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来的时候也迟到了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.65,0:07:52.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为鼻炎去看了医生
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.96,0:07:54.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像是因为室内灰尘什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.97,0:07:56.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦  现代病
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.66,0:07:58.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那可真不得了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.94,0:08:00.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,掌中老虎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.55,0:08:04.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那家伙和栉枝实乃梨是朋友么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.29,0:08:07.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,遭受惨状的明明是我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.37,0:08:08.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.16,0:08:11.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦  还好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.59,0:08:12.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.65,0:08:15.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好厉害啊  逢坂同学和高须同学
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.51,0:08:17.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然掌中老虎很强大呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.51,0:08:19.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是高须同学只是外表可怕而已
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.43,0:08:20.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,并不是不良少年
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.48,0:08:21.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是这样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.46,0:08:23.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,误会好像很快就解开了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.92,0:08:25.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大河？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.55,0:08:27.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.68,0:08:30.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没  没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.54,0:08:32.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,高  高须同学
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.77,0:08:35.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是不是对自己的前途有些迷惘呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.61,0:08:37.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但但  但是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.82,0:08:41.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,志愿调查表除了你以外大家都交了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.70,0:08:44.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起  不小心…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.43,0:08:45.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.48,0:08:48.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不应该说你是对自己的前途迷茫的单亲不良学生对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.71,0:08:49.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,像我这样不知深浅…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.48,0:08:54.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这么晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.40,0:08:56.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,限时销售要结束…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.39,0:09:17.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没  没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.87,0:09:19.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.77,0:09:22.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,书包书包
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.68,0:09:26.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总…总之放着别管吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.13,0:09:31.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你你在干什么什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.36,0:09:31.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.38,0:09:33.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你看  我只是拿书包…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.21,0:09:35.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那…那是你的书包吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.44,0:09:37.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的座位是那旁边的…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.33,0:09:40.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难  难道说列…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.47,0:09:42.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,列列列…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.36,0:09:44.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,列…列弄错了！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.16,0:09:50.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为…为什么抢我的书包
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.51,0:09:55.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  适可而止…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.45,0:10:02.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.15,0:10:03.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.96,0:10:07.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,逢坂？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.36,0:10:18.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.29,0:10:22.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,乱七八糟
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.22,0:10:27.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,乱七八糟
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.35,0:10:43.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸呢  在天国里哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.98,0:10:45.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是个好帅的人哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.86,0:10:47.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说是为了不用担心被刺杀
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.50,0:10:49.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在肚皮上放着一本周刊杂志
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.98,0:10:51.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我被电到了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.80,0:10:53.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是因为跟你相像
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.41,0:10:57.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对我来说可是个大麻烦呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.98,0:11:00.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果不是长着这张脸的话
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.95,0:11:02.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家就不会怕我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.04,0:11:05.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也不会被掌中老虎缠上了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.36,0:11:08.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,应该对自己更有自信才对
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.75,0:11:10.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样的话
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.01,0:11:14.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,志愿调查表
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.15,0:11:17.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.47,0:11:21.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,北村祐作大人收
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.59,0:11:25.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,逢坂…大河
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.06,0:11:28.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.65,0:11:33.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个  放错地方了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.87,0:11:35.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,里面的东西没看过
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.36,0:11:37.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也完全想不出是什么内容
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.81,0:11:39.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘛  还给你好了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.75,0:11:41.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不妙
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.84,0:11:43.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要重新粘回去才行
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.31,0:11:48.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.71,0:11:49.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道说
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.79,0:11:52.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,非常笨？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.76,0:11:56.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,睡觉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.02,0:12:11.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦？  泰子？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.03,0:12:15.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像还不到回来的时候吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.39,0:12:18.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好  让我们继续喝下去哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.13,0:12:20.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs20}高须泰子  花名-未罗乃  工作中
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.54,0:12:19.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好样的  小未罗乃
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.28,0:12:24.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.34,0:12:29.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,窗户…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.34,0:12:34.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好痛！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.79,0:12:42.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什  什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.69,0:12:48.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦？  这个尺寸…好像在哪里…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.02,0:13:04.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,逢坂
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.50,0:13:09.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给我用面纸！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.16,0:13:13.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.10,0:13:19.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什  什  什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.30,0:13:20.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,干
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.31,0:13:21.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.33,0:13:22.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.21,0:13:23.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.49,0:13:26.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给我忘掉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.65,0:13:29.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么给我忘掉…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.17,0:13:30.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  那封…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.94,0:13:32.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,信…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.16,0:13:36.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那东西既然被你知道了  我就已经没脸活下去了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.15,0:13:38.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只有一死了之了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.34,0:13:40.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那为什么要杀的是我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.43,0:13:43.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为我不想死  所以只好把你杀了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.75,0:13:46.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要不然  就把记忆全部抹除掉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.01,0:13:47.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么可能
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.18,0:13:52.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没问题  只要用这个用力敲打脑门
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.44,0:13:56.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算不会断气  至少可以让记忆消失得一干二净
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.38,0:13:57.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要消失啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.63,0:13:59.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给我听好了  那封信…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.36,0:14:00.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吵死了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.77,0:14:03.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吵死了  吵死了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.50,0:14:05.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你看过了吧  读过了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.33,0:14:07.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所  所以说那个是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.64,0:14:08.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不听
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.85,0:14:13.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以  那封情…情书的事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.73,0:14:15.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给我忘掉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.96,0:14:17.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,里面是空的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.79,0:14:24.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,空…的？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.00,0:14:27.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊  所以别说内容了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.52,0:14:31.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,反倒应该说还没交给北村真是太幸运了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.73,0:14:33.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没暴出这样的失态
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.13,0:14:37.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂…喂
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.05,0:14:48.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你到底饿到什么程度了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.01,0:14:54.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,便利店已经吃腻了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.40,0:14:55.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,便利店？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.61,0:14:57.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么你父母不给你做…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.17,0:15:01.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,家家都有一本难念的经吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.39,0:15:02.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拿去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.78,0:15:11.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你当时要是乖乖把书包给我就不会这样了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.22,0:15:14.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你到底要怎么给我善后
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.24,0:15:15.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,脸上还粘着哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.08,0:15:23.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被你这种为了让炒饭的油染上大蒜味的而出生的家伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.57,0:15:25.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.70,0:15:36.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,情…情书哪里丢脸了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.67,0:15:39.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听好了  那可不是值得羞耻的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.35,0:15:40.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你等我一下
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.67,0:15:44.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.06,0:15:47.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这些是什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.75,0:15:52.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这些是什么你明白吗  你不会明白的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.17,0:15:58.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fsp-1}那个是以「如果我要为喜欢的女孩子举行演唱会」为主题而做的列表
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.56,0:16:01.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是为了她而即兴作的诗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.34,0:16:05.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和她一起出去兜风时听的MD  当然没有驾照
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.68,0:16:07.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,里面还根据春夏秋冬不同季节有四种主题
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.42,0:16:10.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么样  恶心死了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.55,0:16:14.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为没有告白的勇气  所以只有这样妄想
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.61,0:16:16.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这的确很没出息
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.55,0:16:18.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但也不觉得这是羞耻
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.55,0:16:20.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以你可以拿出自信来了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.73,0:16:24.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是只在那里妄想  而是已经打算付诸于行动了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.84,0:16:26.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要想得更积极一点啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.50,0:16:28.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,清爽地  开朗地
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.16,0:16:30.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「献给栉枝实乃梨小姐」
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.27,0:16:32.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对  就像栉枝实乃梨一样…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.42,0:16:36.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你居然对实乃梨…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.59,0:16:38.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是嚣张
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.48,0:16:40.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是不自量力
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.88,0:16:43.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啰嗦  你也没资格说别人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.44,0:16:45.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么啊  不是让你忘掉的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.60,0:16:49.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啰  啰嗦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.67,0:16:51.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,冷  冷死了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.03,0:16:54.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起啊  小鹦  吵醒你了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.75,0:16:56.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你给我看什么啊  真恶心
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.91,0:16:59.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说什么  对我家重要的家人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.37,0:17:02.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦！  很好  小鹦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.81,0:17:04.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快向客人做自我介绍
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.55,0:17:06.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天终于说出自己的名字了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.76,0:17:10.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鹦…鹉…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.51,0:17:19.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不  今天的小鹦不在状态上
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.49,0:17:22.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  已经这个时间了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.19,0:17:25.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总之我们是一丘之貉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.11,0:17:28.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那件事不会和任何人说的  相信我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.63,0:17:29.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.26,0:17:30.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.70,0:17:32.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再说你都吃过饭了  快给我回去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.90,0:17:34.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不  请你快回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.32,0:17:36.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我那某种意义上「有病」的妈妈要回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.40,0:17:39.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不  要  啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.00,0:17:42.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我还不相信你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.60,0:17:47.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且…呐  情书到底怎么样呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.31,0:17:50.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在不流行了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.48,0:17:52.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么在这种时候扭扭捏捏的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.98,0:17:55.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恋爱咨询的话以后随时都可以
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.60,0:17:58.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是已经不早了明天再说  好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.45,0:18:02.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的？你愿意帮助我吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.23,0:18:04.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我做  我做我做我做  什么都做
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.18,0:18:06.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么都做哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.79,0:18:08.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会像狗一样的忠诚
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.05,0:18:11.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了我什么都听从？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.56,0:18:12.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我做  我发誓
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.43,0:18:17.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以就这样吧  好吗  好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.87,0:18:26.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这家伙怎么从窗户进来的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.33,0:18:26.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再见
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.89,0:18:28.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我送你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.75,0:18:30.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用了  反正很近
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.53,0:18:31.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且我也带着木刀
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.69,0:18:33.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不  那样才是危险的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.43,0:18:35.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说  那个洞…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.02,0:18:41.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那种程度随便找点纸糊上去就可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.40,0:18:43.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.29,0:18:45.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不介意的话就用这个吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.78,0:18:49.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果要花钱的话  之后我会付的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.09,0:18:52.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明天见了  龙儿
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.41,0:18:53.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦…哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.45,0:18:59.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚才是不是直接叫了我名字
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.55,0:19:18.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你好  我是高…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.21,0:19:19.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快点过来  你不是发誓…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.27,0:19:27.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.68,0:19:28.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你挂断了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.71,0:19:32.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快点过来是去哪里啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.78,0:19:39.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阳台上  为什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.49,0:19:43.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.58,0:19:46.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你答应过会像狗一样什么都做吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.82,0:19:48.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等  等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.34,0:19:51.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,昨天那个是指关于你和北村的事我会帮忙
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.53,0:19:52.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不来的话会怎么样你明白吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.23,0:19:54.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在就让你明白也行
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.96,0:19:57.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用了  那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.97,0:19:59.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再等我十分钟
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.79,0:20:02.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,杂烩饭还有十分钟就煮好了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.27,0:20:03.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,三？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.02,0:20:13.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也要吃吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.37,0:20:33.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真强大
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.83,0:20:41.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打…打扰了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.10,0:20:42.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.93,0:20:45.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,门…门开着
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.17,0:20:50.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是什么气味
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.77,0:20:52.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,逢…逢坂同学
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.75,0:20:54.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我进来了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.32,0:20:57.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好特别的气味…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.30,0:21:06.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,逢坂！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.17,0:21:09.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,逢坂
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.96,0:21:10.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,逢坂
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.83,0:21:11.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,逢坂
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.42,0:21:14.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请让我  请务必让我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.01,0:21:18.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打扫这里的厨房！！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.09,0:21:26.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么啊  回笼觉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.60,0:21:32.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就像做出来的一样
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.88,0:21:37.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,睡着的逢坂真的就像一个人偶
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.05,0:21:39.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有生活感的这间屋子
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.24,0:21:42.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就像是过家家用的道具
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.79,0:21:47.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是  作为人偶的屋子尺寸也太大了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.98,0:21:53.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有十五分左右吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.62,0:21:56.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.15,0:22:17.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.97,0:22:22.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哟
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.83,0:22:25.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然还在打扫中
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.39,0:22:26.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大致已经干净了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.40,0:22:28.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真够呛的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.66,0:22:30.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,水槽的积水都发臭了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.65,0:22:34.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,排水沟里全是粘液霉菌和发臭的垃圾  简直就是地狱绘图
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.71,0:22:36.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,房间里也到处都是灰尘
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.35,0:22:40.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不法侵入  而且还强制打扫
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.77,0:22:42.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有没有自觉啊  你这条狗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.22,0:22:43.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,狗？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.01,0:22:46.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  这样说对狗太失礼了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.29,0:22:48.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,同样是狗你也是劣等狗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.56,0:22:49.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,劣  等  狗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.95,0:22:52.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,何等不知感恩的女人
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.24,0:22:53.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人家特地…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.62,0:23:04.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  「我开动了」呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.40,0:23:10.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大米之神  各位生产者  我开动了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.12,0:23:13.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.59,0:23:17.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说起来不流鼻涕了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.50,0:23:21.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是因为变干净了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.19,0:23:23.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你刚才说什么了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.36,0:23:23.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啰嗦
Dialogue: 0,0:24:56.54,0:24:59.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,乱七八糟的协定  产生的误解  遗传因子的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:25:00.08,0:25:03.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大河  你真是个让人感到佩服的笨蛋啊
Dialogue: 0,0:25:03.49,0:25:05.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,闭嘴  然后给我烂掉吧
